            <title>[SOLR-472] SolrResourceLoader calls normalizeDir twice on when the input instanceDir is null</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-472</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Minor nit I noticed while looking at the SolrResourceLoader:&lt;br/&gt;
When the instanceDir is null upon constructing a SolrResourceLoader, normalizeDir is called twice, once by locateInstanceDir, and then again in the constructor.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch to follow that also adds some docs on it and a simple unit test, etc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
